      <p id="Par43">The <italic>R</italic> code used for the simulation is available as <xref rid="MOESM1" ref-type="media">Supplementary Material</xref>. An additional simulation was conducted to evaluate the performance of the proposed methodology when there are no covariates involved, the details and results of this simulation can also be find in the Supplementary Material (Appendix A, Table <xref rid="MOESM1" ref-type="media">S2</xref>).</p>
